casebody.data:
WOODCLIFF LAKE INVESTORS I, LLC, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
PLANNING BOARD OF THE BOROUGH OF WOODCLIFF LAKE, Borough of Woodcliff Lake, and Borough of Woodcliff Lake Mayor and Council, a Municipal Corporation of the State of New Jersey, Defendants-Respondents. C-318 September Term 2018
081486 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 16, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003692-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
